{"tid":934045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【魚與熊掌】德國「警花」被上司照肺 警察模特兒工作只准二揀一","createTime":"2018-12-09T03:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T04:09:16.000Z","uid":212399,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f208f87bd15dbd3874910e0cc838da28d400736","tid":934045,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"德國一名女警天生麗質，是警隊中的「警花」，她希望兼職任網紅模特兒，不過上司不滿她為發展副業請假半年，急召她回去訓話，還要她在「警察和模特兒工作之間二擇其一」。<br />\n來自薩克森州（Saxony）的34歲警女科萊薩爾（Adrienne Koleszar），於兩年前獲得「最美女警」稱號。今年她申請了6個月的無薪假期，全職發展網紅事業，在Instagram上分享她去旅行、做健身和穿泳裝的照片，「我沒有接受州政府的津貼，我花自己的積蓄，以網紅的工作賺錢。」原定明年1月1日結束假期復職。<br />\n但本周她被上司召見，被告知要在警察和模特兒工作中選擇一項，必須在1月回來全職當警察，否則便辭職，理由是薩克森州急需警察人手，現在還有1000個人手空缺，上司並不希望有警員發展模特兒副業。<br />\n科萊薩爾稱兩邊的工作她都喜歡，不過明白人生裡，不可能想要甚麼都得到，她將會在周一決定，重返警隊還是當全職網紅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181208/large/1544262646_58cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181208%2Flarge%2F1544262646_58cd.jpg&h=b336b11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科萊薩爾有「最美警花」之稱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181208/large/1544262812_647a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181208%2Flarge%2F1544262812_647a.jpg&h=fedf3503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科萊薩爾兼職當網紅。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181209/59006973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59006973&d=4gEoGWe1J0D0L6lGFTmSVuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=01fae499\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59006973&h=8e493dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181209/59006973</a>"},{"pid":"81bb1eed2733a6973272d1c8485e6a8f332d1b7e","tid":934045,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844dd1e114f368e5e361ac2b78ffeeefbc91c375","tid":934045,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"做網紅啦，起碼冇生命危險"},{"pid":"51e75d75df3275ebf9b5fb9a03548ed4a82f27fc","tid":934045,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"當警廁ok"},{"pid":"50fe527a6671f3393fa083ff1959d28355edbf93","tid":934045,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:31:49.000Z","msg":"咁撚老"},{"pid":"b299ce2fe623d16b9f5747daa24aa4e41653b59f","tid":934045,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03faa82822416ee49bb4f737ef02f4ce53116c2","tid":934045,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97JnSNb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97JnSNb.png&h=59e24cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d37965f1f3afd9362064bb239d41b2321285dc4e","tid":934045,"uid":9387,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"手瓜粗過連登仔"},{"pid":"0ff523ee82e69197c55fa7b6e998dc001a33b686","tid":934045,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"一係出去做，一係係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24d85c964b76d2b886d8ce33f0764a6cb9a6de8","tid":934045,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"好似4張嘢"},{"pid":"d8fd1ab09b8b60bb002491c32f077a0779b552cb","tid":934045,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"粗重野